lly characterize its simplest case of two partial premises.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Feb 2010 10:02:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 26 Jun 2010 22:44:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-14"}
